The paper discusses the detection of cyber attacks in industrial control systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed method uses neural networks, which suggests the paper could also belong to the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with control systems, which could also place it in the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
